{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777081227843,"sessionID":"ses_23db5c505ffejriSGWcGAD1vQd","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"background_output","callID":"call_r3acNxHd4qKTowQqCruwQVu4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"block":false,"full_session":false,"include_thinking":false,"include_tool_results":false,"message_limit":20,"since_message_id":"","task_id":"bg_38e909cd","thinking_max_chars":2000,"timeout":60000},"output":"Task Result\n\nTask ID: bg_38e909cd\nDescription: Explore task-hall code\nDuration: 33s\nSession ID: ses_23db51d28ffe1SbCGzwMlOf47d\n\n---\n\nThe `task-hall` package is a lifecycle management system for agent tasks, following the `frontdesk-v0.2` protocol. It manages tasks from request to completion via a centralized \"hall\" but does not perform execution or scheduling itself.\n\n### Key Scripts and Files\n- **`cli.package.json`**: Registry for all `mycli task-hall` commands (init, claim, tasks, show, etc.).\n- **`scripts\\task-hall.ps1`**: The core PowerShell implementation for all hall operations.\n- **`state\\listings.json`**: The central index of all tasks and their current status.\n- **`state\\tasks\\{task_id}\\task.md`**: The task definition, including requirements and the \"领取门槛\" (Claim Threshold).\n- **`README.md`**: Contains the design specs, model tier definitions (`nano` to `expert`), and the task report protocol.\n\n### Implementation Status\n- **Operational**: `submit-request`, `claim`, `review-submission`, and status tracking are fully functional.\n- **Protocols**: Uses `frontdesk-v0.2` for ingestion/claims and `reviewer-v0.1` for submission audits.\n- **Agents**: Integrated with `opencode/task-hall-frontdesk` and `opencode/task-hall-reviewer` for semantic validation.\n- **Current Data**: `listings.json` shows several tasks in `done` or `draft` status, currently tested primarily by `opencode/private-assistant`.\n\n### Analysis Agent Decision Factors\n- **Complexity & Tier**: A task's `task.md` specifies a `min_model_tier` (e.g., `strong`). An agent must verify its own tier against this.\n- **Claim Protocol**: Claims are validated by the frontdesk agent. Agents should use a `claim.json` with their `model_tier` and `claim_reason`.\n- **Visibility**: Default `tasks` command only shows `listed` (unclaimed) tasks. Use `tasks all` to see full history.\n- **Success Criteria**: Tasks are moved to `done` only after a `review-submission` (audit of the `task-report.md`) or a manual `submit success`.","metadata":{"truncated":false,"task_id":"bg_38e909cd","agent":"Sisyphus-Junior","category":"quick","description":"Explore task-hall code","sessionId":"ses_23db51d28ffe1SbCGzwMlOf47d"},"title":"quick - Explore task-hall code","time":{"start":1777081227833,"end":1777081227843}},"id":"prt_dc24b991d002FA6OYwAFTOSnPX","sessionID":"ses_23db5c505ffejriSGWcGAD1vQd","messageID":"msg_dc24b7bcf001F0wNohp3fV5uQd"}}
